description: Argentine Gourmet Empanadas in ChicagoWe make the most delicious Gourmet Empanadas around.Different to other empanadas which are deep fried, ours are oven baked to keep its original flavor and your heart healthy.Fifty Four Eleven is a premium brand founded by three Argentine friends from diverse professional backgrounds as Economics, Business Administration, Marketing and Advertising. Fifty Four Eleven stands for quality, simplicity and a sense of fun!Empanadas are one of the most traditional dishes served in Argentina. Just walk the trendy city of Buenos Aires and you’ll be able to find at least two or three “casas de empanadas” (house of empanadas) per block.  Empanadas are served at parties, business meetings, as a starter, as a main course or in festivals. They can be found in the most humble house as well as in the most glamorous cocktail party.
name: 5411 Empanadas
